      "updated": 1772351219519,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "CareerGenie AI is a Generative AI platform that helps job seekers prepare effectively by\nanalyzing resumes and job descriptions. It identifies strengths and weaknesses, generates\nrelevant technical and behavioral interview questions, and builds a personalized preparation\nroadmap along with tailored resumes.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "CareerGenie AI is a Generative AI platform that helps job seekers prepare effectively by analyzing resumes and job descriptions. It identifies strengths and weaknesses, generates relevant technical and behavioral interview questions, and builds a personalized preparation roadmap along with tailored resumes.",
